        "answer":":question \\\\ \\text{ si } ${:x}=\\color{red}{${math.fractionSimplifiee(-:b[0],:a[0])}} \\text{ ou } ${:x}=\\color{red}{${math.fractionSimplifiee(-:b[1],:a[1])}}",
